title: Vegan Food Stall
description: Possibly named "Thi Neung Aharn Jay", and located at the Government Complex building, near the Immigration department, there are 2 large food courts. One of them has a pure veg (vegan) food stall. Offers basic Thai vegan dishes for 40-60 baht each. The owners used to operate UR Station in Suan Pluu when the main immigration service was there.
streetAddress: Government Complex Building B, Chaengwattana Road Soi 7, Laksi
